---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2026-05-20';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms"
  description="Spark & Anvil terms of service."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
    <h1 class="font-brand font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-anvil mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-anvil/60 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </section>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
    <p class="text-anvil/50 italic">
      Placeholder. Full terms of service drafted by counsel before public launch.
      Will cover: app licensing (one-time purchase, perpetual personal use), website
      use, intellectual property, disclaimers appropriate for kid-safe context,
      and dispute resolution.
    </p>
    <p class="text-anvil/80 leading-relaxed mt-6">
      Until the full version ships, our use of the apps and website is governed by
      Apple&apos;s App Store terms (apps) and standard practice (website).
      For questions: <a href="mailto:legal@spark-and-anvil.com">legal@spark-and-anvil.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
